cost optimization using S3 Lifecycle rules by transitioning data between S3 storage classes ‚Äî a powerful way to reduce storage costs without deleting your data.
‚úÖ What is an S3 Lifecycle Rule?
An S3 Lifecycle Rule automates:
Transition: Moving data to a cheaper storage class after a certain time.
Expiration: Deleting data after it is no longer needed.
S3 Standard, S3 Intelligent-Tiering, S3 Standard-IA, S3 One Zone-IA, S3 Glacier, S3 Glacier Deep Archive
