Q. Linked Accounts vs Member Accounts
--> AWS billing ‡§Æ‡§ß‡•ç‡§Ø‡•á, Linked Accounts ‡§Ü‡§£‡§ø Member Accounts ‡§Ø‡§æ ‡§¶‡•ã‡§® ‡§∂‡§¨‡•ç‡§¶‡§æ‡§Ç‡§ö‡§æ ‡§Ö‡§∞‡•ç‡§• ‡§¨‡§π‡•Å‡§§‡•á‡§ï‡§¶‡§æ ‡§è‡§ï‡§ö ‡§Ö‡§∏‡§§‡•ã, ‡§™‡§£ ‡§§‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§Ç‡§ö‡§æ ‡§µ‡§æ‡§™‡§∞ ‡§ï‡•ã‡§£‡§§‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ AWS service ‡§ö‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ ‡§∏‡§Ç‡§¶‡§∞‡•ç‡§≠‡§æ‡§§ ‡§ï‡•á‡§≤‡§æ ‡§Ü‡§π‡•á ‡§Ø‡§æ‡§µ‡§∞ ‡§•‡•ã‡§°‡§æ‡§∏‡§æ ‡§´‡§∞‡§ï ‡§™‡§°‡§§‡•ã. ‡§π‡•á ‡§¶‡•ã‡§®‡•ç‡§π‡•Ä concepts Consolidated Billing (‡§è‡§ï‡§§‡•ç‡§∞‡§ø‡§§ ‡§¨‡§ø‡§≤‡§ø‡§Ç‡§ó) ‡§Ü‡§£‡§ø AWS Organizations ‡§Æ‡•Å‡§≥‡•á ‡§Ø‡•á‡§§‡§æ‡§§.
Consolidated Billing (‡§è‡§ï‡§§‡•ç‡§∞‡§ø‡§§ ‡§¨‡§ø‡§≤‡§ø‡§Ç‡§ó) Concept
Imagine your company has many teams (Dev, QA, Production) and each team uses a separate AWS Account.

Main Idea: Instead of paying for 5-10 separate bills, ‡§§‡•Å‡§Æ‡•ç‡§π‡•Ä ‡§è‡§ï‡§æ‡§ö ‡§†‡§ø‡§ï‡§æ‡§£‡•Ä (account) ‡§∏‡§ó‡§≥‡•á bills ‡§≠‡§∞‡§§‡§æ.

1. Management Account (‡§ï‡§ø‡§Ç‡§µ‡§æ Payer Account)
‡§ï‡§æ‡§Ø ‡§Ö‡§∏‡§§‡•á? (What is it?)
‡§π‡§æ ‡§Æ‡•Å‡§ñ‡•ç‡§Ø Account ‡§Ö‡§∏‡§§‡•ã, ‡§ú‡•ã ‡§∏‡§ó‡§≥‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ billing ‡§ö‡•á payment ‡§ï‡§∞‡§§‡•ã.
‡§Ø‡§æ‡§≤‡§æ Payer Account ‡§∏‡•Å‡§¶‡•ç‡§ß‡§æ ‡§Æ‡•ç‡§π‡§£‡§§‡§æ‡§§.
‡§Ø‡§æ account ‡§Æ‡§ß‡•ç‡§Ø‡•á ‡§ï‡•ã‡§£‡§§‡•á‡§π‡•Ä actual workload (EC2 instances, S3 buckets) ‡§®‡§∏‡§§‡§æ‡§§; ‡§π‡•á ‡§´‡§ï‡•ç‡§§ financial governance ‡§∏‡§æ‡§†‡•Ä ‡§µ‡§æ‡§™‡§∞‡§≤‡•á ‡§ú‡§æ‡§§‡•á.
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. Linked Accounts (‡§ú‡•Å‡§®‡•á ‡§®‡§æ‡§µ)
‡§ï‡§æ‡§Ø ‡§Ö‡§∏‡§§‡•á? Management Account ‡§∏‡•ã‡§¨‡§§ link ‡§ï‡•á‡§≤‡•á‡§≤‡•á accounts. ‡§Ø‡§æ‡§Ç‡§ö‡•á  billing management account ‡§Æ‡§ß‡•ç‡§Ø‡•á consolidate (‡§è‡§ï‡§§‡•ç‡§∞) ‡§π‡•ã‡§§‡•á.
‡§π‡•á term AWS Organizations ‡§Ø‡•á‡§£‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§™‡•Ç‡§∞‡•ç‡§µ‡•Ä ‡§ñ‡•Ç‡§™ ‡§µ‡§æ‡§™‡§∞‡§æ‡§§ ‡§π‡•ã‡§§‡§æ.
Billing Role: ‡§π‡•á account services (resources) ‡§µ‡§æ‡§™‡§∞‡§§‡•á, ‡§™‡§£ ‡§¨‡§ø‡§≤ management account ‡§≤‡§æ ‡§ú‡§æ‡§§‡•á.
------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. Member Accounts (‡§®‡§µ‡•Ä‡§® ‡§Ü‡§£‡§ø Standard ‡§®‡§æ‡§µ)
‡§ï‡§æ‡§Ø ‡§Ö‡§∏‡§§‡•á? (What is it?)
‡§ú‡•á‡§µ‡•ç‡§π‡§æ ‡§§‡•Å‡§Æ‡•ç‡§π‡•Ä AWS Organizations setup ‡§ï‡§∞‡§§‡§æ, ‡§§‡•á‡§µ‡•ç‡§π‡§æ Management Account ‡§µ‡§ó‡§≥‡§§‡§æ ‡§¨‡§æ‡§ï‡•Ä‡§ö‡•á ‡§∏‡§∞‡•ç‡§µ accounts Member Accounts ‡§Æ‡•ç‡§π‡§£‡•Ç‡§® ‡§ì‡§≥‡§ñ‡§≤‡•á ‡§ú‡§æ‡§§‡§æ‡§§.
Member Account ‡§Ü‡§£‡§ø Linked Account ‡§π‡•á same thing ‡§Ü‡§π‡•á, ‡§´‡§ï‡•ç‡§§ Member Account ‡§π‡•á AWS Organizations ‡§ö‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ modern terminology ‡§®‡•Å‡§∏‡§æ‡§∞‡§ö‡•á ‡§®‡§æ‡§µ ‡§Ü‡§π‡•á.

Core Principle :
Billing Consolidated (‡§¨‡§ø‡§≤‡§ø‡§Ç‡§ó ‡§è‡§ï‡§§‡•ç‡§∞‡§ø‡§§): Member Accounts ‡§ö‡•á charges Management Account ‡§≤‡§æ ‡§ú‡§æ‡§§‡§æ‡§§.
Resource Isolation (‡§∏‡§Ç‡§∏‡§æ‡§ß‡§® ‡§µ‡§ø‡§≤‡§ó‡•Ä‡§ï‡§∞‡§£): ‡§™‡•ç‡§∞‡§§‡•ç‡§Ø‡•á‡§ï Member Account ‡§§‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ‡§Ç‡§ö‡•á resources (EC2, S3, RDS) ‡§∏‡•ç‡§µ‡§§‡§Ç‡§§‡•ç‡§∞‡§™‡§£‡•á (independently) manage ‡§ï‡§∞‡§§‡•á. ‡§è‡§ï‡§æ Member Account ‡§Æ‡§ß‡•Ä‡§≤ team ‡§¶‡•Å‡§∏‡§±‡•ç‡§Ø‡§æ Member Account ‡§Æ‡§ß‡•Ä‡§≤ resources ‡§™‡§æ‡§π‡•Ç ‡§∂‡§ï‡§§ ‡§®‡§æ‡§π‡•Ä, ‡§ú‡•ã‡§™‡§∞‡•ç‡§Ø‡§Ç‡§§ permissions ‡§¶‡§ø‡§≤‡•á ‡§ú‡§æ‡§§ ‡§®‡§æ‡§π‡•Ä‡§§.
